data.description: Gorgeous stone fireplace in the great room w/ wood floors. Charming kitchen w/ stainless still appliances & breakfast bar. Huge 4 bedrooms upstairs & bonus room. Primary bedroom separate from other bedrooms. Lavish primary bathroom w/ double sink vanity, sitting area, separate garden tub & standing glass shower. Enjoy the evenings on the great back deck or covered patio w/ fire pit !! Enormous backyard w/ privacy fence & storage shed!!
